<h3 id="winery">Winery</h3>
<p>Goldeneye is Duckhornâ€™s Pinot Noir project and began making premium quality, cool-climate Pinot Noir from their estate winery in the Anderson Valley since 1997. Blending grapes from four estate vineyards, they are dedicated to crafting wines of refinement and elegance from a rich palette of terroir-inspired fruit. Reflecting the Mendocino Coastâ€™s unique marine influences, sites, and soils, these grapes create rich, full-flavored Pinot Noir</p>
