<h3 id="region">Region</h3>
<p><strong>Anderson Valley, California</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>1996
    <ul>
      <li>Goldeneye is founded in the Anderson Valley with the purchase of an 80-acre ranch that includes a small winery and vineyard.
        <ul>
          <li>Located at the headwaters of the Navarro River</li>
          <li>Ideal clay soils</li>
          <li>Marine-influenced climate offering long, mild days and cooling fog and winds</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
